This is Fac-Stemi
=====================================


Goal is simple : generate factures using LT's templates from structured data.

Example :

Request
-------

POST : 
Content-type : application/json
Body : {
	"client" : {
		"name" : "VIDAL",
		"address" : "27 rue camille desmoulins"
	},
	"invoice" : [{
		"days" : 25,
		"daily_rate" : 450,
		"tax_rate" : 19.6 // defaults to 19.6
	}, { ... }]
}

Response
--------

201 CREATED 
Content-type: application/json
Body : {
	"id" : "LT-255",
	"published" : true // published in google drive directory
}
